title: Mood Rating (IPC Session 1)
description: Mood Rating form that is intended for IPC Session 1

item.text:
Tip #1
The purpose of the Mood Rating Scale is to help clients sort through what happens in their lives that affect their mood.

Tip #2
Help the client make the explicit link between mood and events.

Example dialogue
"Let's check in on how you have been feeling."
On a scale of 1 to 10, with 1 being the worst mood and 10 being the best mood, how have you been feeling in the past week?

extension.valueString: ¿Cómo te has sentido en la última semana?
On a scale of 1 to 10, with 1 being the worst mood and 10 being the best mood, how have you been feeling in the past week?
